body:
I made this plugin to diversify the game mechanics and make the game more difficult. In this plugin, there are only **9 types of skills**. From the names, you can already guess what they will do

## Woodcutting
(You can't use certain types of axes until the required level) - To level up, you need to chop down trees;

## Mining
(You can't use certain types of pickaxes until the required level) - To level up, just dig in the mines;

## Combat
(You can't use certain types of swords until the required level) - To level up, kill monsters;

## Vitality
(You can't use certain types of armor sets until the required level) - To level up, you need to take damage;

## Intellect
(You can't use an enchanted table until a certain level) - To level up, you need to gain experience;

## Wonderer
(It doesn't limit anything but gives a buff) - To level up, just run around the world;

## Crafting
(It doesn't limit anything but gives a buff) - To level up, you need to make items on a workbench;

## Cooking
(It doesn't limit anything but gives a buff) - To level up, just fry food in the oven;

## Building
(It doesn't limit anything but gives a buff) - To level up, you need to place blocks

I know that my plugin has a lot of errors and if you encounter them, write to the **Discord channel** I will try to answer and fix them as quickly as possible.
